seo: Goby DnsLog, 插件, DNS检测, 漏洞扫描
seo_en: Goby DnsLog, plugin, DNS detection, vulnerability scanning
summary: 该插件通过Goby DnsLog进行DNS检测，生成唯一的DNS域名并获取解析记录，用于发现可能的漏洞或风险。
summary_en: This plugin uses Goby DnsLog for DNS detection, generating unique DNS domains and retrieving resolution records to identify potential vulnerabilities or risks.
